<section id="getting.maven">
	<title>Getting Bundlor with Maven</title>
	<para>Eclipse Virgo Bundlor can be obtained from a Maven repository</para>
	<orderedlist>
		<listitem>
			<para>
				Add the SpringSource Enterprise Bundle Repository resolvers to the <literal>pom.xml</literal> file
			</para>
			<programlisting language="xml">&lt;repository&gt;
  &lt;id&gt;com.springsource.repository.bundles.@release.type@&lt;/id&gt;
  &lt;url&gt;http://repository.springsource.com/maven/bundles/@release.type@&lt;/url&gt;
&lt;/repository&gt;</programlisting>
		</listitem>
	</orderedlist>
</section>